#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:2
msgid "SSRF"
msgstr "SSRF"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:6
msgid ""
"服务端请求伪造（Server Side Request Forgery, "
"SSRF）指的是攻击者在未能取得服务器所有权限时，利用服务器漏洞以服务器的身份发送一条构造好的请求给服务器所在内网。SSRF攻击通常针对外部网络无法直接访问的内部系统。"
msgstr "Server-Side Request Forgery (SSRF) means that when an attacker has not obtained full control of a server, they exploit a server-side vulnerability to send a crafted request as the server to the internal network where the server resides. SSRF attacks usually target internal systems that cannot be accessed directly from external networks."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:9
msgid "漏洞危害"
msgstr "Impact"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:10
msgid "SSRF可以对外网、服务器所在内网、本地进行端口扫描，攻击运行在内网或本地的应用，或者利用File协议读取本地文件。"
msgstr "SSRF can be used to perform port scanning against external networks, the server's internal network, and the local host; attack applications running on the internal network or locally; or read local files through the file protocol."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:12
msgid "内网服务防御相对外网服务来说一般会较弱，甚至部分内网服务为了运维方便并没有对内网的访问设置权限验证，所以存在SSRF时，通常会造成较大的危害。"
msgstr "Compared with Internet-facing services, internal services are generally less hardened. Some internal services do not even enforce authentication for internal access to simplify operations and maintenance, so SSRF vulnerabilities often cause significant impact."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:15
msgid "利用方式"
msgstr "Exploitation Methods"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:16
msgid "SSRF利用存在多种形式以及不同的场景，针对不同场景可以使用不同的利用和绕过方式。"
msgstr "SSRF can be exploited in many forms and scenarios. Different exploitation and bypass methods can be used for different scenarios."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:18
msgid "以curl为例, 可以使用dict协议操作Redis、file协议读文件、gopher协议反弹Shell等功能，常见的Payload如下："
msgstr "Using curl as an example, the dict protocol can be used to operate Redis, the file protocol can read files, and the gopher protocol can trigger a reverse shell. Common payloads are as follows:"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:31
msgid "相关危险函数"
msgstr "Related Dangerous Functions"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:32
msgid ""
"SSRF涉及到的危险函数主要是网络访问，支持伪协议的网络读取。以PHP为例，涉及到的函数有 ``file_get_contents()`` / "
"``fsockopen()`` / ``curl_exec()`` 等。"
msgstr "Dangerous functions involved in SSRF are mainly network access functions and network-reading functions that support pseudo-protocols. In PHP, for example, related functions include ``file_get_contents()`` / ``fsockopen()`` / ``curl_exec()``."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:35
msgid "过滤绕过"
msgstr "Filter Bypass"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:38
msgid "更改IP地址写法"
msgstr "Change the IP Address Representation"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:39
msgid "一些开发者会通过对传过来的URL参数进行正则匹配的方式来过滤掉内网IP，如采用如下正则表达式："
msgstr "Some developers filter internal IP addresses by applying regular expressions to the incoming URL parameter, for example by using the following regular expressions:"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:41
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``^10(\\.([2][0-4]\\d|[2][5][0-5]|[01]?\\d?\\d)){3}$``"
msgstr "``^10(\\.([2][0-4]\\d|[2][5][0-5]|[01]?\\d?\\d)){3}$``"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:42
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``^172\\.([1][6-9]|[2]\\d|3[01])(\\.([2][0-4]\\d|[2][5][0-5]|[01]?\\d?\\d)){2}$``"
msgstr "``^172\\.([1][6-9]|[2]\\d|3[01])(\\.([2][0-4]\\d|[2][5][0-5]|[01]?\\d?\\d)){2}$``"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:43
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``^192\\.168(\\.([2][0-4]\\d|[2][5][0-5]|[01]?\\d?\\d)){2}$``"
msgstr "``^192\\.168(\\.([2][0-4]\\d|[2][5][0-5]|[01]?\\d?\\d)){2}$``"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:45
msgid "对于这种过滤我们采用改编IP的写法的方式进行绕过，例如192.168.0.1这个IP地址可以被改写成："
msgstr "This kind of filtering can be bypassed by rewriting the IP address representation. For example, the IP address 192.168.0.1 can be rewritten as:"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:47
msgid "8进制格式：0300.0250.0.1"
msgstr "Octal format: 0300.0250.0.1"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:48
msgid "16进制格式：0xC0.0xA8.0.1"
msgstr "Hexadecimal format: 0xC0.0xA8.0.1"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:49
msgid "10进制整数格式：3232235521"
msgstr "Decimal integer format: 3232235521"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:50
msgid "16进制整数格式：0xC0A80001"
msgstr "Hexadecimal integer format: 0xC0A80001"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:51
msgid "合并后两位：1.1.278 / 1.1.755"
msgstr "Merge the last two parts: 1.1.278 / 1.1.755"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:52
msgid "合并后三位：1.278 / 1.755 / 3.14159267"
msgstr "Merge the last three parts: 1.278 / 1.755 / 3.14159267"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:54
msgid "另外IP中的每一位，各个进制可以混用。"
msgstr "In addition, different bases can be mixed for each part of the IP address."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:56
msgid "访问改写后的IP地址时，Apache会报400 Bad Request，但Nginx、MySQL等其他服务仍能正常工作。"
msgstr "When accessing a rewritten IP address, Apache returns 400 Bad Request, but other services such as Nginx and MySQL can still work normally."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:58
msgid "另外，0.0.0.0这个IP可以直接访问到本地，也通常被正则过滤遗漏。"
msgstr "In addition, the IP address 0.0.0.0 can directly access the local host and is also commonly missed by regex-based filters."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:61
msgid "使用解析到内网的域名"
msgstr "Use a Domain Name That Resolves to an Internal Address"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:62
msgid "如果服务端没有先解析IP再过滤内网地址，我们就可以使用localhost等解析到内网的域名。"
msgstr "If the server does not resolve the IP address before filtering internal addresses, domain names such as localhost that resolve to internal addresses can be used."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:64
msgid ""
"另外 ``xip.io`` "
"提供了一个方便的服务，这个网站的子域名会解析到对应的IP，例如192.168.0.1.xip.io，解析到192.168.0.1。"
msgstr "In addition, ``xip.io`` provides a convenient service where subdomains resolve to the corresponding IP address. For example, 192.168.0.1.xip.io resolves to 192.168.0.1."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:67
msgid "利用解析URL所出现的问题"
msgstr "Abuse URL Parsing Issues"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:68
msgid "在某些情况下，后端程序可能会对访问的URL进行解析，对解析出来的host地址进行过滤。这时候可能会出现对URL参数解析不当，导致可以绕过过滤。"
msgstr "In some cases, backend programs parse the requested URL and filter the parsed host address. Improper parsing of URL parameters may then make it possible to bypass the filter."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:70
msgid ""
"比如 ``http://www.baidu.com@192.168.0.1/`` "
"当后端程序通过不正确的正则表达式（比如将http之后到com为止的字符内容，也就是www.baidu.com，认为是访问请求的host地址时）对上述URL的内容进行解析的时候，很有可能会认为访问URL的host为www.baidu.com，而实际上这个URL所请求的内容都是192.168.0.1上的内容。"
msgstr "For example, with ``http://www.baidu.com@192.168.0.1/``, if the backend parses the URL with an incorrect regular expression, such as treating the characters from after http up to com, namely www.baidu.com, as the requested host address, it may conclude that the URL host is www.baidu.com. In reality, the content requested by this URL comes from 192.168.0.1."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:73
msgid "利用跳转"
msgstr "Use Redirects"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:74
msgid "如果后端服务器在接收到参数后，正确的解析了URL的host，并且进行了过滤，我们这个时候可以使用跳转的方式来进行绕过。"
msgstr "If the backend server correctly parses the URL host after receiving the parameter and applies filtering, redirects can be used to bypass the check."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:76
msgid ""
"可以使用如 http://httpbin.org/redirect-to?url=http://192.168.0.1 "
"等服务跳转，但是由于URL中包含了192.168.0.1这种内网IP地址，可能会被正则表达式过滤掉，可以通过短地址的方式来绕过。"
msgstr "Services such as http://httpbin.org/redirect-to?url=http://192.168.0.1 can be used for redirection. However, because the URL contains an internal IP address such as 192.168.0.1, it may be filtered by a regular expression, so a short URL can be used to bypass the filter."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:78
msgid "常用的跳转有302跳转和307跳转，区别在于307跳转会转发POST请求中的数据等，但是302跳转不会。"
msgstr "Common redirects include 302 and 307 redirects. The difference is that a 307 redirect forwards data in a POST request, while a 302 redirect does not."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:81
msgid "通过各种非HTTP协议"
msgstr "Use Various Non-HTTP Protocols"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:82
msgid "如果服务器端程序对访问URL所采用的协议进行验证的话，可以通过非HTTP协议来进行利用。"
msgstr "If the server-side program validates the protocol used by the requested URL, non-HTTP protocols can be used for exploitation."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:84
msgid "比如通过gopher，可以在一个url参数中构造POST或者GET请求，从而达到攻击内网应用的目的。例如可以使用gopher协议对与内网的Redis服务进行攻击，可以使用如下的URL："
msgstr "For example, through gopher, a POST or GET request can be constructed in a URL parameter to attack internal applications. For instance, the gopher protocol can be used to attack an internal Redis service with the following URL:"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:90
msgid ""
"除了gopher协议，File协议也是SSRF中常用的协议，该协议主要用于访问本地计算机中的文件，我们可以通过类似 "
"``file:///path/to/file`` "
"这种格式来访问计算机本地文件。使用file协议可以避免服务端程序对于所访问的IP进行的过滤。例如我们可以通过 "
"``file:///d:/1.txt`` 来访问D盘中1.txt的内容。"
msgstr "In addition to the gopher protocol, the file protocol is also commonly used in SSRF. This protocol is mainly used to access files on the local computer, and local files can be accessed with a format such as ``file:///path/to/file``. Using the file protocol can avoid server-side filtering of the accessed IP address. For example, ``file:///d:/1.txt`` can be used to access the contents of 1.txt on drive D."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:93
msgid "DNS Rebinding"
msgstr "DNS Rebinding"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:94
msgid "一个常用的防护思路是：对于用户请求的URL参数，首先服务器端会对其进行DNS解析，然后对于DNS服务器返回的IP地址进行判断，如果在黑名单中，就禁止该次请求。"
msgstr "A common defense approach is as follows: for a user-supplied URL parameter, the server first performs DNS resolution, then checks the IP address returned by the DNS server. If the IP address is on a blacklist, the request is blocked."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:96
msgid "但是在整个过程中，第一次去请求DNS服务进行域名解析到第二次服务端去请求URL之间存在一个时间差，利用这个时间差，可以进行DNS重绑定攻击。"
msgstr "However, in this process there is a time gap between the first DNS resolution request and the later server-side request to the URL. This time gap can be used to perform a DNS rebinding attack."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:98
msgid ""
"要完成DNS重绑定攻击，我们需要一个域名，并且将这个域名的解析指定到我们自己的DNS Server，在我们的可控的DNS "
"Server上编写解析服务，设置TTL时间为0。这样就可以进行攻击了，完整的攻击流程为："
msgstr "To perform a DNS rebinding attack, a domain name is needed, and its resolution must be delegated to a DNS server under our control. On that controllable DNS server, implement the resolution service and set the TTL to 0. The full attack flow is then:"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:100
msgid "服务器端获得URL参数，进行第一次DNS解析，获得了一个非内网的IP"
msgstr "The server obtains the URL parameter, performs the first DNS resolution, and obtains a non-internal IP address."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:101
msgid "对于获得的IP进行判断，发现为非黑名单IP，则通过验证"
msgstr "The server checks the obtained IP address and, finding that it is not on the blacklist, allows it."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:102
msgid "服务器端对于URL进行访问，由于DNS服务器设置的TTL为0，所以再次进行DNS解析，这一次DNS服务器返回的是内网地址。"
msgstr "The server accesses the URL. Because the DNS server's TTL is set to 0, DNS resolution is performed again, and this time the DNS server returns an internal address."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:103
msgid "由于已经绕过验证，所以服务器端返回访问内网资源的结果。"
msgstr "Because validation has already been bypassed, the server returns the result of accessing the internal resource."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:105
msgid "随着 DNS Rebinding 技术不断发展，也有一些新的攻击方式："
msgstr "As DNS Rebinding techniques continue to develop, some newer attack methods have also appeared:"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:107
msgid "一个响应中，同时回复多个IP请求，包含公网和内网IP"
msgstr "Return multiple IP addresses in a single response, including both public and internal IP addresses."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:108
msgid "对于浏览器同时请求A记录和AAAA记录的情况，先回复合法的IPv6地址，一段时间后回复内网IPv4地址"
msgstr "When the browser requests both A and AAAA records, first return a legitimate IPv6 address, then return an internal IPv4 address after a period of time."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:111
msgid "利用IPv6"
msgstr "Use IPv6"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:112
msgid ""
"有些服务没有考虑IPv6的情况，但是内网又支持IPv6，则可以使用IPv6的本地IP如 ``[::]`` ``0000::1`` "
"或IPv6的内网域名来绕过过滤。"
msgstr "Some services do not account for IPv6, while the internal network supports it. In that case, IPv6 local IP addresses such as ``[::]`` and ``0000::1``, or internal domain names over IPv6, can be used to bypass filtering."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:116
msgid "利用IDN"
msgstr "Use IDN"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:117
msgid ""
"一些网络访问工具如Curl等是支持国际化域名（Internationalized Domain "
"Name，IDN）的，国际化域名又称特殊字符域名，是指部分或完全使用特殊的文字或字母组成的互联网域名。"
msgstr "Some network access tools, such as Curl, support Internationalized Domain Names (IDN). Internationalized domain names are also called special-character domain names, meaning Internet domain names composed partially or entirely of special characters or letters."

#: ../../source/vuln/ssrf.rst:119
msgid ""
"在这些字符中，部分字符会在访问时做一个等价转换，例如 ``ⓔⓧⓐⓜⓟⓛⓔ.ⓒⓞⓜ`` 和 ``example.com`` "
"等同。利用这种方式，可以用 ``① ② ③ ④ ⑤ ⑥ ⑦ ⑧ ⑨ ⑩`` 等字符绕过内网限制。"
msgstr "Among these characters, some are converted to equivalent characters during access. For example, ``ⓔⓧⓐⓜⓟⓛⓔ.ⓒⓞⓜ`` is equivalent to ``example.com``. This can be used with characters such as ``① ② ③ ④ ⑤ ⑥ ⑦ ⑧ ⑨ ⑩`` to bypass internal-network restrictions."

